text: The service and food surpassed my expectations. Their Mookata provided a great variety of food and an excellent customer experience . I ordered food items and a chicken soup. The aroma of the soup and food is appetising. The seafood and meat are fresh. I would strongly recommend everyone try their marinated meat and seafood because they are tender and delicious. Lastly , the pricing is reasonable due to the excellent food quality and customer service.

best fish i have ever eaten in sg, extremely flavorful and can tell that they never cheap out on the spices and ingredients.

iberico pork and marinated chicken are must try for the mookata, tomyam soup base also taste good

the fish is absolute gas vro. Like, first bite in, and my taste buds straight-up ascended to another dimension.
Staff are the GOAT, so swag. Felt their aura from miles away. They're super chill and friendly, literally made me feel like the main character from the moment I walked in.
Overall vibe? 11/10, would happily pull up to a mookata sesh just for this fish. Legit, no crumbs left. Big W.

Must try iberico pork and Thai salt baked fish.

Service and atmosphere is fantastic.
SIGMA, ABSOLUTE SIGMA. I WOULD COME BACK AGAIN . OBVIOUSLY FOR THE FOOD AND THE SERVICE. THE AURA WHEN I WENT ABSOLUTE AURA MOVEMENT. 100/10 RECOMMENDED !
